<div>
  <style>
    .resume-makr-recovery-email {
      width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  </style>

  <div id="resume-makr-recovery-email" class="resume-makr-recovery-email">
    <h1>Reset Your Password</h1>

    <div>
      You told us you forgot your password. If you really did, click here to
      choose a new one:
    </div>

    <button type="button">Choose a New Password</button>

    <div>
      If you didnâ€™t mean to reset your password, then you can just ignore this
      email; your password will not change.
    </div>

    <hr />

    <div>"Choose a New Password" button not working?</div>
    <div>Just copy and paste this link in your browser:</div>
    <%
      url = Application.get_env(
          :web, :front_end_url
        ) <> "/reset/" <> assigns[:token]
    %>
    <a href="<%= url %>"><%= url %></a>
  </div>
</div>
